title: Available 1 Bed 1 Bath
posting_body: ['Austin, 78758', 'Esperanza Crossing', '$1807', '1 Bedroom', 'These apartments feature a living room, dining room, and a kitchen with standard appliances, standard countertops, a dishwasher, and disposal.', 'There is hardwood flooring in the kitchen, living room, dining room, and bathroom(s) with carpet in the bedroom(s) throughout the home.', 'The bedroom(s) have a closet and the bathroom(s) include a soaking tub.', 'Features central A/C, central heat, ceiling fans, nine foot ceilings, and closets for additional storage.', 'Select units include nest thermostat, quartz style countertops, stainless steel appliances, fireplace, and a private balcony/patio.', 'Cable and internet ready.', 'Full-sized washer/dryer in select units or washer/dryer connections.', 'Community amenities include a resort style swimming pool with a sundeck and spa, dog park, pet wash station, fire pit, bbq lounge, sand volleyball court, playground, clubhouse, fitness center, yoga room, gaming room, on-site laundry facility, recycling, pet play area, grills, and courtyard.', 'UTILITIES.', 'Short term leases are available.', 'Pets are welcome.', 'Off-street unassigned lot parking included in the rent.', 'Covered parking available.', 'Less than a ten-minute commute to Interstate 35.', 'PHOTOS ARE AN EXAMPLE OF SIMILAR UNITS WITHIN THE BUILDING, ACTUAL UNIT MAY VARY.', '***Availability and pricing is real-time, can change daily, and varies by lease term***', 'Contact Agent:', 'Dave Burroughs', 'Independent Agents Austin TX', 'show contact info', '<', 'Follow us on Twitter @RentalBeast', 'Find us on Facebook: <URL>']
